videos.description: Charles Matthews lobs it up for Jon Teske who throws it down all over a Purdue defender.
videos.headline: Teske catches a lob - and body - on alley-oop slam

videos.description: Ignas Brazdeikis creates separation from his defender, steps back and nails a 3 to extend Michigan's lead over Purdue.
videos.headline: Brazdeikis does James Harden impression on step-back 3

videos.description: Jordan Poole goes baseline and finishes with a nice reverse lay up in traffic.
videos.headline: Poole goes baseline for a reverse

videos.description: Jon Teske extends Michigan's lead to 67-50 after hitting a 3 from the top of the key.
videos.headline: 7-foot-1 Teske knocks in a 3
